name: Custom made paper backdrop for a woodland, boho, rustic  wedding, party or photoshoot
description:
This listing is for a backdrop made to cover a 12ft x 8ft surface. The backdrop is made from white water paper cones and brown twine.

The order includes 45 individual strands, which measure between 4ft- 9ft.  The gaps between the water cones vary, giving the backdrop a beautiful flowing effect. 

The backdrop is delivered assembled and ready for you to install at your chosen location.

This backdrop is perfect for weddings, set designs, boutique store front or at special event's backdrop for photos.

Custom requests are most welcome. I will happily make a backdrop to suit your needs. 

If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact me.

name: Kewtie Kuddlers
description:
Kewtie Kuddlers were inspired by the announcement of my first grandchild due to arrive in 2016.  

As a child, my own grandmother did crochet and the memories of working crochet with her provided additional inspiration.  Each Kewtie Kuddler is made with soft washable yarn and is sized to fit your newborn Kewtie up to age 6 months.  Each set is crafted with love and adorned with buttons handed down by my mother and grandmother.  

My wish is for you to cherish your Kewtie as much as I anticipate cherishing mine!  lisa

*Photos are current colors available.  More coming soon.  Want a specific color? I have many options to choose from.
